settings.para: US patented Silicon formula. Perfected by our exclusive Heritage Concentrate™ proprietary process to unleash the power of your own collagen.
Horsetail is one of our plant-based raw silica sources of silicic acid. Our horsetail extract method eliminates thiaminase enzymes, ensuring our formula's safety and purity.
Rosemary extract is a natural preservative that is derived from the rosemary plant. It is made from rosemary leaves and has antioxidant properties.
Reverse osmosis (RO) water is a type of filtered water that has gone through a purification process called reverse osmosis. This results in highly purified water.

settings.richt1:
Designed to supplement your daily silica intake. It's especially beneficial for those who may not obtain sufficient silica from their regular dietary sources. The maintenance dose is 15 mL, to be taken 15 minutes before a meal holding the product for a minute or two under the tongue to improve the absorption.  

Great for promoting glowing skin, hair & nails.
settings.richt2:
The intensive dosage is the recommended intake for individuals wanting to see faster results or starting the silica for the first time. The intensive loading dosage includes 30 mL to 60 mL per day, to be taken 15 minutes before a meal. The dosage should be divided into two shots , for example, two 15 mL shots. 

Great for supporting healthy bones & joints.

settings.heading: Why LIVING SILICA® is the most effective form of silica?
settings.row_content: Bioavailability measures the extent to which a nutrient can be used by cells in the body. No other colloidal silica, silicic acid, or plant extract-based silica supplements in the marketplace provide higher bioavailability than LIVING SILICA®. This superior bioavailability is attributed to our Heritage Concentrate™ proprietary process. This one-of-a-kind method ensures that the silica in our product is in a form that your body can absorb effectively. When you absorb more silica into your body, you’re able to generate more collagen.* The issue is that most people consume collagen to experience its ultimate effects. LIVING SILICA® helps our bodies promote healthy collagen production without the need for consumption, offering a full spectrum of benefits that positively affect our energy, stress levels, and more!

settings.heading: The importance about incorporating LIVING SILICA®
settings.row_content: By adding LIVING SILICA®to your daily routine,you can support the optimal levels of silica your body needs to thrive at its best. Silica is an essential trace mineral required for the production of collagen, elastin, keratin, and glycosaminoglycans (GAGs). These elementscontribute to tissue hydration, elasticity, and strength, helping you look and feel your best every day.* LIVING SILICA® promotes healthy skin cells, supports collagen, and aids in cell turnover with hyaluronic acid to keep your hair, skin, and nails looking vibrant and healthy.

settings.heading: What´s different about Plant-Based Collagen Booster?
settings.row_content: Our plant-based version of LIVING SILICA®, sourced from natural horsetail, utilizes silica from botanical extracts. LIVING SILICA® Plant-Based Collagen Booster (previously known as 'G5 Siliplant') is primarily composed of silica, which is then purified and stabilized by an organic compound to enhance absorption. LIVING SILICA® is fully assimilable by the body’s cells, providing safe, natural silica in liquid form.

settings.heading: The uniqueness about LIVING SILICA®
settings.row_content: LIVING SILICA® is a doctor-formulated, professional-grade supplement designed to support your natural healthy collagen production. Formulated in 1994 by Sc. D. Loïc Le Ribault, and with more than 30 years in the market, LIVING SILICA® pioneered a proprietary process known as Heritage Concentrate™. Heritage Concentrate™is theproprietary process used across all LIVING SILICA® products. It raises the solubility limit of silicon (Si) and maintains it in a small, monomeric, and well-absorbed form for optimal intestinal absorption. This unique process ensures that you get the most out of every dose of LIVING SILICA®, making it the perfect addition to your daily health routine.
